  "remarks": "\nNikita Petrovich Busel is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because Busel is: 1) working as director of a Government of Russia – affiliated entity, namely State Grain Operator State Unitary Enterprise, and therefore obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia.\n",
